column1: Let's set up the party now!
Yes, yes. There are still so many people left to invite.
Wow, so energetic... Shouldn't youkai be sleeping at this hour?
Sorry to say, but I have something more important to do right now.

because we are starting the party right away!
I will seriously hurt you if you hinder me, you know?
On this magical shooting star night,
This isn't good! It seems that I have no choice but to exterminate you.
